assesmentMethods.en:
Contact teaching 100 h, independent work 62 h.
Assessed by participation in contact teaching or according to what has been agreed upon.
At least 80% participation in face-to-face teaching is mandatory to complete the course. If, due to absences, the student does not achieve the learning outcomes defined in the course description, the remaining 20% may have to be compensated as determined by the responsible teachers of the course. All absences must be reported to the teachers in charge.&nbsp;The responsible teachers of the course will specify the necessary compensating assignments.
